text: Christine Clarke (born 11 August 1960) is a Canadian rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Scarborough, Toronto Category:Rowers from Toronto
